msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-24 12:18am-10:18pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/koCRIVY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkoCRIVY.png&h=4a7e0e05&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6Cz4cp2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6Cz4cp2.png&h=e6bfc3fe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(15)梁凱寧vs李施嬅(5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"7cdcff33780091a28a521bafd3d43e698afbc371","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":18,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-24 12:20am-10:20pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AijgxTQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAijgxTQ.png&h=534faf99&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AxdyTZq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAxdyTZq.png&h=4bbab68f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(13)車泳希vs朱晨麗(2)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"49f003e4c687c7f415469ea66b22546467728481","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-24 12:22am-10:22pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/feOuBG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfeOuBG4.png&h=65c3d702&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FeugAOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFeugAOc.png&h=af2fef71&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(12)陳逸敏vs杜如風(18)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"fb740177fd5ac0a3f26529bb6ec9562943565a6b","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由17年12月25日始至18年1月12日為本季歇冬期,屆時將會無任何比賽等大家可以休息一下<br />\n下半季賽程安排將於元旦官宣,敬請留意<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/499662/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/499662/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃十六強抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/500805/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/500805/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強抽籤直播及結果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">16強賽序(前者先主場):<br />\nElizabeth Olsen v IU <br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月13日 3月7日 <br />\n<br />\nJennifer Lawrence v 周子瑜@TWICE<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月13日 3月7日 <br />\n<br />\nGal Gadot v 林娜璉@TWICE<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月14日 3月6日 <br />\n<br />\n唐嫣 v 新垣結衣<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月21日 3月13日 <br />\n<br />\n朱千雪 v 長澤正美<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月14日 3月6日 <br />\n<br />\nEmma Watson v 林宣妤<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月21日 3月13日 <br />\n<br />\n謝安琪 v 名井南@TWICE<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月20日 3月14日 <br />\n<br />\n平井桃@TWICE v 林明禎<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月20日 3月14日 </span>"},{"pid":"fcc1769edb4cd099045b425fa33112e44943f07a","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff3ba2dca9486e0431aaefd10b0d87b388eada2","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eb14e6a5e0618471155e22b22abaf78a10a359","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5166c4ce2ec7b7a4362248c3171ea214c667f41e","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59faf6af5f48c6ba88af56d13b775988041a10b","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T17:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b24922c22656b656a99d4870f0e6eb7ef811c5","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b041cc7792516c675bbedb61b7de76da88b8da5c","tid":507852,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T20:07:32.000Z"